how make DOS:
1- Co-cfc.in
2- Comando Bash: pw.x -i Co-cfc.in | Co-cfc.out
3- dos.in
4- dos.x < dos.in > dos.out
5- extract data from dos.out and run in python, the code are in archieve DOS.py

Also you can vary the values of distances between atoms, so calculate the values where converges the cut energy. Here what you have to do:

1- First you need automatization the Co-cfc.in varing the "a" paramenter, this code are in archieve Co-cfc.bash

